<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وهو في <span class="c1">" مشيخة ابن طهمان "</span> <span class="c2">(٢٣٨ / ٢)</span> .<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
